<p><strong>Wait But Why: </strong>Without the limitations of the other formats, this is where the drawings can be displayed full-size, where footnotes can be interactive, etc. The downside here is that you can only read it on a tablet or phone, not an e-reader, and there’s no dark mode at the moment (we’re working on that for later in 2023). Available <a href="https://waitbutwhy.com/wop">here</a>.</p>
